Maintainer: Ruiqiu Chan <reachu.chan@outlook.com>
Description: 
    CAIScore implements an ensemble‐based framework for quantifying gene set activity 
    in single‐cell or bulk transcriptomic data. It integrates five complementary scoring 
    algorithms—AUCell, UCell, singscore, single‐sample GSEA (ssGSEA via GSVA), and 
    Seurat’s AddModuleScore—then optionally scales and aggregates them into a unified 
    composite score for robust pathway or module analysis.
